{"word":"G2121 - εὔκαιρος - eúkairos - yoo'-kahee-ros - Convenient","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὔκαιρος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eúkairos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">yoo'-kahee-ros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Convenient</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தக்க, ஏற்ற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"seasonable, timely, opportune"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2095 - εὖ - eû - yoo/2095\">G2095</a> and <a href=\"#/G2540 - καιρός - kairós - kahee-ros'/2540\">G2540</a>; <i>well timed</i>, that is, <i>opportune:</i> - convenient, in time of need.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G170/170\">G170</a>, <a href=\"#/G171/171\">G171</a>, <a href=\"#/G2120/2120\">G2120</a>, <a href=\"#/G2121/2121\">G2121</a>, <a href=\"#/G2122/2122\">G2122</a>, <a href=\"#/G2540/2540\">G2540</a>, <a href=\"#/G4340/4340\">G4340</a>"}]}